# ─── Per-machine dev-tool scratch files ──────────────────────────────────
# Editor + AI-assistant scratch state. Per-developer; never tracked.
CLAUDE.md
.claude/
.cursor/
.cursorrules
.aider*

# ─── Dev scratch screenshots (root-level, underscore-prefixed) ────────────
# Throwaway UI captures taken while iterating (e.g. _mdi_tabbed.png). Kept out
# of both repos — name any keeper screenshot without the leading underscore.
/_*.png

# ─── .NET / Visual Studio / Rider build artefacts ──────────────────────────
bin/
obj/
# `dotnet publish` output and release zips — large, regenerable.
# (Inline comments after a pattern aren't valid in .gitignore — Git treats
#  the whole line as the pattern. Keep the comment on its own line.)
publish/
*.user
*.suo
*.userprefs
*.pidb
*.swp
*.DotSettings.user
.vs/
.vscode/
.idea/
*.csproj.cache
*.csproj.FileListAbsolute.txt
*.cache

# ─── NuGet package state (path leakage on TSR-Jason machine) ──────────────
*.nupkg
*.snupkg
*.nuget.cache
*.nuget.dgspec.json
*.nuget.g.props
*.nuget.g.targets
project.assets.json
project.nuget.cache
[Pp]ackages/

# ─── OS junk ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# ─── Genie 5 runtime data (per-machine, not for the repo) ─────────────────
# Recordings: raw XML captures from live sessions — contains other players'
# speech, character data, login state. Must NEVER be in the public repo.
test_results/
Logs/
*.log

# Per-character profiles: encrypted passwords, character names, layout
# state. Lives in {AppData}/Genie5/Profiles/ at runtime. The rule is
# anchored to the repo root with the leading slash so it only catches a
# stray runtime profiles dir copied to the top level — NOT the legitimate
# source folder at src/Genie.Core/Profiles/ that defines ConnectionProfile,
# ProfileStore, ProfileCrypto. (The unanchored form, "Profiles/", silently
# shadowed those source files for a week before another machine's build
# surfaced the bug.)
/Profiles/
profiles.json
display.json
paths.json

# Maps: user-edited local map data. The official source-of-truth is
# github.com/GenieClient/Maps. We ship a migration that pulls from there;
# we don't ship maps in this repo.
Maps/
*.xml.backup

# ─── Reference repos (third-party source for design study) ────────────────
# We clone Genie 4 + Lich 5 + Mudlet etc. into _refs/ for cross-reference
# while building Genie 5. They have their own licenses; don't ship them
# embedded in this repo.
_refs/

# ─── Agent / IDE context ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Per-developer agent project memory and IDE state — contains personal
# notes, in-progress checkpoints, character references, etc. Each
# contributor keeps their own.
.claude/
.cursor/
.aider*
CLAUDE.local.md

# ─── Old sandbox + replay-test artefacts ──────────────────────────────────
# Older sandbox outputs from before TestHarness + the new src/ layout were
# in place. Kept locally for reference but not for the public repo.
files/
replay_*.txt
*_raw.cs
ScriptEngine_raw.cs
ScriptExpression_raw.cs
ScriptParser_raw.cs

# ─── Secrets & credentials ────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Belt-and-braces — nothing in source today, but defense-in-depth for
# any future credential/config files.
*.env
.env*
secrets.json
credentials.json
appsettings.Development.json
appsettings.*.local.json
*.pfx
*.key
*.pem
